There is a general effect of convergence to the robots. There might also be a condition effect: people only converge to the robot in the Gaze Aversion condition, but the AIC of the models suggests that the model without condition is better.

Mediation analysis (f0 ~ intimacy + intensity)

(see tutorial here: https://towardsdatascience.com/doing-and-reporting-your-first-mediation-analysis-in-r-2fe423b92171)

Intimacy does seem to affect f0 directly, independently of intensity.
